ome.smuggler.core.service.imports

Interface ImportRequestor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ImportTrigger

    public interface ImportRequestor
    Triggers an OMERO import.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods Default Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      default ImportId enqueue(ImportInput request)
      Adds the import request to the queue and returns immediately.
      ImportBatch enqueue(java.util.stream.Stream<ImportInput> requests)
      Adds the import requests to the queue and returns immediately.

    • Method Detail

      • enqueue

        default ImportId enqueue(ImportInput request)
        Adds the import request to the queue and returns immediately. The request will subsequently be fetched from the import queue and serviced as needed. What is added to the queue is an instance of QueuedImport.
        Parameters:
        request - details what to import.
        Returns:
        a token to use to get hold of this import run, for example to get some feedback on progress.
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if the argument is null.

      • enqueue

        ImportBatch enqueue(java.util.stream.Stream<ImportInput> requests)
        Adds the import requests to the queue and returns immediately. The requests will subsequently be fetched from the import queue and serviced as needed. What is added to the queue is an instance of QueuedImport for each import request.
        Parameters:
        requests - detail what to import.
        Returns:
        an object with all the QueuedImports, each having its own ImportId through which you can get hold of the corresponding import run, for example to get some feedback on progress.
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if the stream or any of its elements is null.
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the stream is empty.
